{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-jsx","path":"/projects/risotto-play/","result":{"data":{"post":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/2adcb/risotto-play.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/ba381/risotto-play.webp 200w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/7f61c/risotto-play.webp 400w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/d00b9/risotto-play.webp 800w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/92f8c/risotto-play.webp 1200w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/fad48/risotto-play.webp 1600w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/90d15/risotto-play.webp 1984w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/772e8/risotto-play.png 200w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/e17e5/risotto-play.png 400w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/5a190/risotto-play.png 800w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/c1b63/risotto-play.png 1200w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/29007/risotto-play.png 1600w,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/2adcb/risotto-play.png 1984w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/5a190/risotto-play.png\"\n          alt=\"Risotto Play\"\n          title=\"Risotto Play\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sometime back in 2018, a friend of mine started building his own programming language, \"Risotto\" <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://github.com/risotto/risotto\" title=\"(GitHub link)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">(GitHub link)</a> (although I wanted the name to be \"Ravioli\" so the syntax could be \"Ravioli Ravioli, give me the formuoli\" <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9r8Swai8_g&feature=youtu.be&t=32\" title=\"(lol I know I'm immature)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">(lol I know I'm immature)</a>, but I digress).</p>\n<p>Anywho, I've enjoyed using services such as <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://goplay.space/\" title=\"The Go Play Space\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">The Go Play Space</a> and <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://repl.it/\" title=\"Repl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Repl</a> in the past, and wanted to replicate this kind of environment (whilst paying 0 for hosting) for Risotto.</p>\n<h2><a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://api.play.risotto.dev\" title=\"The API\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">The API</a></h2>\n<p>This runs on <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://kubesail.com/\" title=\"Kubesail\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Kubesail</a> for easy K8s deployment (and the free tier), with the API written in Go, and spawning a process running the code passed to it.</p>\n<p>In order to keep the API service performant, there's a little bit of IP addressed rate limiting, and runtime constraints, but overall the traffic is low enough that this hasn't come close to being an issue yet.</p>\n<p>The API is designed so that if anyone wants, they can use it for their own purposes, which is highly encouraged (get Risotto out there!)</p>\n<p>It is also covered with Unit Tests, and automatic CI/CD.</p>\n<h2><a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://play.risotto.dev\" title=\"The UI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">The UI</a></h2>\n<p>This is hosted with <a class=\"siteLink\" href=\"https://pages.github.com/\" title=\"GitHub pages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">GitHub pages</a> for easy CI/CD and just fantastic performance.</p>\n<p>Written in React (TypeScript flavour), it's fairly simple but is optimised for responsive design and even has a cute little \"Share\" feature, so you can share your creations with others.</p>","excerpt":"Sometime back in 2018, a friend of mine started building his own programming language, \"Risotto\"  (although I wanted the name to be \"Ravioli\" so the syntax could be \"Ravioli Ravioli, give me the…","fields":{"slug":"/projects/risotto-play/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🍲 Risotto Play","date":"2020-04","tech":["Go","TypeScript","React"],"link":"https://play.risotto.dev/","source":"https://github.com/risotto/play-ui","previewImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":1200,"height":940,"src":"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/f3583/risotto-play.png","srcSet":"/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/f3583/risotto-play.png 1x,\n/static/0a94121047e0867afed8b20f523645b1/bbee5/risotto-play.png 1.5x"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/risotto-play/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/about/aboutMe/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"👨‍💻 About me"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/projects/ipfs-web-hosting/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"📦 IPFS Web Hosting"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["602281340","682078843"]}